      "content": "It signals to the health store that the source should report periodically on this property; if it doesn't, then there must be something wrong with the watchdog.",
      "pos": [
        21215,
        21375
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The watchdog health is captured by considering the event as error.",
      "pos": [
        21376,
        21442
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "SequenceNumber.",
      "pos": [
        21446,
        21461
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "A positive integer that needs to be ever increasing, as it represents the order of the reports.",
      "pos": [
        21462,
        21557
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "It is used by Health Store to detect stale reports, received late because of network delays or other issues.",
