        22633,
        22859
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The health events are returned by the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>health queries<ept id=\"p1\">](service-fabric-view-entities-aggregated-health.md#health-queries)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        22860,
        22981
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The added metadata contains:",
