      "content": "Health model usage",
      "pos": [
        28426,
        28444
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The health model allows the cloud services and the underlying Service Fabric platform to scale, because the monitoring and health determination is distributed among the different monitors within the cluster.",
      "pos": [
